data.description: Welcome to 1418 Nighthawk LN. , a stunning three bedroom, two bathroom home nestled in the desirable city of Mansfield. This charming residence is located in a beautiful growing neighborhood! Upon entering you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan, that also features a flex space that could be used as a second living area, office, or play area. The well appointed kitchen boasts sleek appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar, making meal preparation a breeze. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom that features a luxurious soaking tub, separate shower, and a dual sink vanity. Two additional generously sized bedrooms provide for plenty of space. Once out back, you'll love the covered patio and the size of the backyard. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home! The roof on this home was replaced in July!
